-- Sphere Gets License for Askaf Mine in Mauritania, AMI Reports
-- B y   O u d a a   M a r o u f
-- 2012-07-13T14:51:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-13/sphere-gets-license-for-askaf-mine-in-mauritania-ami-reports.html
Mauritania awarded an iron-ore
operating license to Sphere Minerals Ltd. for its Askaf project,
Agence Mauritanienne d’Information reported, citing a Council of
Ministers statement after its weekly meeting in Nouakchott, the
capital.  The council also approved amendments to the government’s
oil production-sharing contracts with International Petroleum
Group and a consortium led by Dana Petroleum Plc, the state-
owned agency, known as AMI, said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Oudaa Marouf in Nouakchott at 
